    "ArticleTitle": "Exacerbated type II interferon response drives hypervirulence and toxic shock by an emergent epidemic strain of Streptococcus suis.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "1928",
      "EndPage": "1939",
      "MedlinePgn": "1928-39"
